 



Merck Appoints Bridgette P. Heller As Executive Vice President and President, Consumer Health Care | Business Wire


























































Merck Appoints Bridgette P. Heller As Executive Vice President and 
      President, Consumer Health Care






Former Johnson & Johnson and Kraft Executive Joins Merck










