Insider Activity


Individual




Bridgette P. Heller



Ms. Bridgette P. Heller is Executive Vice President at Danone SA. She is on the Board of Directors at Tech Data Corp. and The ADT Corp. Ms. Heller was previously employed as Executive VP & President-Consumer Health Care by Merck & Co., Inc., President-Baby Global Business Unit by Johnson & Johnson, Managing Partner by Heller Associates, Inc., Executive Vice President & GM-Coffee Division by Kraft Foods, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Chung's Foods, Inc., and Chairman by Girls, Inc. She also served on the board at PCA International, Inc. She received her undergraduate degree from Northwestern University and an MBA from Kellogg School of Management.



