Last Updated: 05/24/2015 



Executive Summary
Heller served as the Executive Vice President at Merck & Co., the nation’s No. 2 drug manufacturer, and President of its Consumer Care Business, which was sold to Bayer AG in 2014. A veteran of some of America’s best-known consumer brands, she began her career by serving in a variety of managerial positions at Kraft Foo 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Heller lives in Princeton, New Jersey, with her husband and two children. She was the recipient of the International Award for Safe Motherhood (2008) from Americans for United Nations Population Fund Heller was the Princeton 
Current Focus
